</taxonomicName>
) in preserved specimen. Colony covered upper part of the stalks, but not around the spiculous anchor. Contracted preserved polyps 1.0–3.0 mm in height, 
<quantity box="[231,364,853,875]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="3.5" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="8" pageNumber="331" unit="mm" value="2.5" valueMax="3.5" valueMin="1.5">1.5–3.5 mm</quantity>
in diameter.
</paragraph>
